rows.label: tev078201_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Arsenican about the planet where he was born.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Arsenican about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0001
rows.name:
If I close my eyes, I can still see its contaminated land
masses and seas of black sludge. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0002
rows.name:
The spoiled wood of its rotted forests reeked as strongly
as the voltant-drenched ruins in its barren wastelands.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0003
rows.name:
It was a paradise that Golbogga created at the same
time he breathed life into the Zaruboggan. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0004
rows.name:
Oh, how I yearn to return home one day! *fsssh*
This world is far too pure for the likes of us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0007
rows.name:
Ahhh, the moment of pure bliss when I submerged
myself into that polluted Noctilum swamp... *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0008
rows.name:
It was a taste I'd not experienced in all the time since
I arrived on this planet. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0009
rows.name:
Sparkling lights burst throughout my brain,
and my entire body seemed to float. *fsssh*
Oh, the ecstasy![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0010
rows.name: *fssssssssssssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0011
rows.name:
Er, I mean... *fsssh* I feel deep remorse for my actions,
and will never trouble my companions like that again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Arsenican about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0012
rows.name:
Now that I've had a chance to tour your
waste-processing units, I have fallen in love
with you humans all over again. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0013
rows.name:
I never would have imagined that so much voltant was
being produced in this city day in and day out! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0014
rows.name:
Please, humans! I beg of you! *fsssh*
You must continue polluting this planet![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0015
rows.name:
Then my people will be able to sup upon the sweet
fruits of devoltanization! *fsssh* Ahhhhh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Arsenican about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_SEL2031
rows.name: Ask Arsenican what he intends to do next.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0016
rows.name:
Yesterday, I had my first opportunity in a long time to
speak with the child I disgorged. *fsssh*
I can't believe how much little Orleron has grown![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0017
rows.name:
Apparently he's become quite close with a human
woman. She taught him to call me "Dad." *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0018
rows.name:
It was a strange feeling. *fsssh* He is truly a part of a
new generation of Zaruboggan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0019
rows.name:
I bet he'll go on to devoltanize more voltant than I or
any of his ancestors. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0023
rows.name:
Compared to Bedun, which the almighty Golbogga
bestowed upon us, this planet is much too pure. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0024
rows.name:
While Mira's purity has long been a source of despair
for me, you have brought hope back to my life. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0025
rows.name:
The incredible speed with which your people produce
voltant is truly inspiring. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0026
rows.name:
Your waste-processing units overflow with more
voltant-drenched garbage than you could ever hope
to dispose of! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0027
rows.name:
I believe that you humans will one day transform Mira
into a foul paradise the equal of Bedun itself! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_SEL3021
rows.name: Ask Arsenican about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0020
rows.name: Thank you for aiding Orleron on his search for voltant.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0021
rows.name:
I understand that by working closely with your people,
he has discovered numerous sources of voltant. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078201_MSG0022
rows.name:
I must confess that I was worried at first, but I am
truly relieved to see what a splendid Zaruboggan
he has become! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]
